```plantuml
@startuml mrubash1_trainspotting

actor User
participant "Raspberry Pi Camera" as Camera
participant "Video_Camera" as VideoCamera
participant "Video_Sensor" as VideoSensor
participant "Video_Detector" as VideoDetector
participant "TensorFlow Model" as TensorFlowModel
participant "Data Storage" as DataStorage

User -> Camera: Start Video Capture
Camera -> VideoCamera: Capture Frame
VideoCamera -> VideoSensor: Add Frame to input_deque

loop Continuous Processing
    VideoSensor -> VideoSensor: Background Subtraction
    VideoSensor -> VideoSensor: Noise Reduction
    VideoSensor -> VideoSensor: ROI Extraction
    VideoSensor -> VideoDetector: Detect Motion

    alt Motion Detected
        VideoDetector -> TensorFlowModel: Classify Object
        TensorFlowModel --> VideoDetector: Classification Result

        alt Object is Train
            VideoDetector -> VideoDetector: Determine Train Direction
            VideoDetector -> DataStorage: Store Detection Event
            VideoDetector -> DataStorage: Store Motion Data
        end
    end

    VideoSensor -> VideoCamera: Adjust Camera Settings (if needed)
    VideoCamera -> Camera: Set New Camera Settings
end

User -> DataStorage: Query Detection Events and Analysis

@enduml
```